							<td valign="top" width="50%">
								<p>ATL<sup>3</sup> is an Atlanta based technology and learning company dedicated to helping children and adults with disabilities learn to use assistive technology. We are dedicated to &quot;finding the right fit&quot; for persons who need assistive technology to be more independent.</p>
								<p>Assistive technology can enhance a child's ability to learn new skills, communicate with others, and complete tasks with more ease. The technology itself is not the cure, but another avenue to more independence and success. The ability for the child and caregiver to use technology to its potential is our goal. Let us help you and your child. Please call for an appointment today.</p>
								<p>ATL<sup>3</sup>, Inc.<br>
									2524 Flair Knoll Drive<br>
										Atlanta, Georgia 30345</p>
								<p>404-697-3182<br>
										404-929-6468 FAX</p>
								<p><a href="mailto:info@at4learning.com">info@at4learning.com</a></p>
